net.opentsdb.utils

Class ByteArrayPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.utils.Pair<byte[],byte[]>
      • net.opentsdb.utils.ByteArrayPair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<ByteArrayPair>

    public class ByteArrayPair
extends Pair<byte[],byte[]>
implements Comparable<ByteArrayPair>
    Simple helper class to store a pair of byte arrays for use in situations where a map or Map.Entry doesn't make sense. Extends the Pair class and overrides the equals method using Bytes.memcmp() to determine if both arrays have the same amount of data in the same order. Sorting is performed on the key first, then on the value.
